{
  "stem": "5430.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Henry Borenstein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a middle name, Hersh, H-E-R-S-H.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Borenstein, B-O-R-E-N-S-T-E-I-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Polish version was B-O-R-E-N-S-Z-T-E-J-N. 'Borenshtain.'",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the name at birth, right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't-- I did not have any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 25, 1924.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 70-- 71-- I'll be 71 in September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Warsaw, Poland on Leszno Street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still remember the name, the number 116 Leszno Street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "L-E-S-Z-N-O Street.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] basically--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My earliest recollection was, I guess, about four or five years old when my father schlepped me to cheder, and of course, I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the cheder was only a couple blocks away, just about a block away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was on also on Leszno Street, corner of Okopovna, O-K-O-P-O-V-N-A.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember looking at the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His first name's Shaya, Shaya Bord.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a beard, and so we called him Shaya Bord.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had long, big eyebrows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was scared stiff at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's about the earliest recollections of my earliest youth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The next thing I remember, all running-- since I was the youngest, my sister was next to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I always used to follow her around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she would chase me away because she would go out with her girlfriends, and I was a little boy, but-- And so the next thing I remember is, I guess it was her birthday party, and I was the cute little brother and always admired by her girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the next thing that I remember was going to public school, which is I guess about--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--eight or nine or maybe a little later because I was going to cheder for about, about four years, yeah.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
